Use your iPad or another computer on your network to control
your Linux desktop. This program will run on the desktop to 
be controlled and uses Node.js to deliver the client through
a web browser.To run, Node.js and xautomation must be installed.

To install Node and xautomation:

sudo apt-get install nodejs
sudo apt-get install xautomation

Then to start the program:

node app.js

St